title: 20 Acre Nature Park, Dog park!
posting_body: A Sports Club at Your Doorstep *
Private 20-acre Nature Park * Three Playgrounds * Licensed Onsite Day Care *

Located just fifteen minutes from the Dallas North Tollway and Belt Line Road, apartment homes offer ceramic tile entry, decorative fireplace, vaulted ceilings, vanities with full-length mirror and full-size washer/dryer connections.
It's like having a sports club at your doorstep.

Spectacular amenities include three pools, wading pool and spa, three playgrounds, golf driving range and putting green, indoor full-court basketball, indoor racquetball, sand and water volleyball, fitness center with HDTV and business center with high-speed Internet.
Covered parking is available as is WiFi in the clubhouse, business center and poolside.
Please call Desiree with Dash Apartment locators
